" the scarlet tide " is a song written by t - bone burnett and elvis costello and performed by alison krauss from the 2003 film cold mountain   according to costello , burnett " always said ' scarlet tide ' was an anti - fear song . "

elvis costello : elvis was nominated for an oscar & a grammy for " the scarlet tide " , a song from this 2003 jude law civil war film

